			Book &amp; Lyrics by Samrat Chakrabarti &amp; Sanjiv Jhaveri<br/>
			Produced by LAUGHistan, LLC</p>
<p>BUMBUG Unplugged, an encore presentation, of a new Rock Opera by Samrat Chakrabarti and Sanjiv Jhaveri, is an electrifying musical reinvention of “A Christmas Carol” told through the looking glass of NYC Immigrants and Hyphenated America. Like so many immigrants, disillusioned Deli-owner Scroogewala left his motherland years ago to pursue the American dream. Amidst his battle with holiday merriment, Scroogewala is visited by a motley crew of misfits who remind him that love, loss and laughter are all a part of that dream he’d almost given up on.</p>
